# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Prediction Market Oracle — Environment Variables
#  Copy to .env for local dev with `deno run --env ...`
#  In Deno Deploy: set via Settings → Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── LLM Keys (at least one required for Agent 3) ──────────
# Groq — free tier, fast inference (recommended)
# Get key: https://console.groq.com
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_groq_key_here

# Zhipu AI GLM — free tier
# Get key: https://open.bigmodel.cn
GLM_API_KEY=your_glm_key_here

# OpenRouter — free models available (fallback)
# Get key: https://openrouter.ai
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-your_openrouter_key_here

# ── Platform ───────────────────────────────────────────────
OWNER_ADDRESS=your_wallet_or_username

# ── Notes ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Agent 1 (CoinGecko)  — no key needed, free public API
# Agent 2 (Binance)    — no key needed, free public API
# Agent 3 (LLM Oracle) — uses GROQ_API_KEY → GLM → OpenRouter
#
# For non-crypto markets (sports, politics) all 3 agents
# use LLM reasoning since there's no simple public API.
